Name: Jumping Over It With Neko Girl
About the game: Jumping Over It With Neko Girl is a Pixel platformer that doesn't forgive mistakes. You have only one way-up! Evaluate your every step, every jump, because any wrong action can be fatal. The higher you go, the longer you will have to fall. Destroy dangerous enemies, enjoy a variety of landscapes drawn in the style of pixel art, and jump! Jump to reach the top. Key Features Simple and convenient operation, it all depends on your skills Five types of dangerous enemies and a boss battle Various locations and dynamic music And cute Neko Girl!!!
